    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a pot (with a matching lid) over a medium-low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once the butter has melted, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and <strong>ground cumin </strong>with your<strong> bulgur wheat </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
